<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #eee;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #197aca;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #197aca;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2 style="color: #197aca">Account Deleted</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>
          We are writing to confirm that your account has been successfully
          deleted as per your request.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your data has been removed from our active systems. If you have any
          questions or if this deletion was made in error, please contact our
          support team immediately.
        </p>
        <p>We're sorry to see you go!</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br />The Sniper Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Mr aqar. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
